174 A.3d 504 THE IRWIN LAW FIRM, P.A., PLAINTIFF-PETITIONER, v. RICHARD GRABOWSKY, DEFENDANT-RESPONDENT.

C-173 September Term 2017

079513 October 16, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-004800-13 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
